room_title: Escape room "The Hangover" by The Escape Room Experience in Laconia
room_address: 555 Main Street Suite A Laconia, NH 03246
room_description:
You’re in fabulous Las Vegas, the biggest party of all. Last night was great... wasn’t it? It’s a shame you can’t remember it. What on earth happened? You have to get it together.
You have to catch a cab to the airport in one hour or you'll miss your flight. You finally figured out what hotel you're in but you can't find your wallet or room key. What are you going to do? You need to escape so that what happened in Vegas truly stays in Vegas!
